                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1162" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0211</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8440 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">演进的蓝图——广州白云山制药总厂的信息系统规划</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王惠芬，叶文晖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">暨南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州白云山制药总厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">演进的蓝图；信息系统规划；组织战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Evolution of the Blueprint; Information System Planning; Organizational Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经历了重组的白云山人认识到企业的定位和发展战略的重要性，更认识到信息系统规划在企业战略中的重要位置。“十一五”期间，总厂紧抓信息化和工业化融合这一主线，大力推进面向集成的信息系统规划，促进信息化和工业化相互渗透、相互融合，先后引进ERP系统、OA系统、BQ商务智能系统等多个系统。2010年，制定了公司“十二五”信息化规划。通过统一的信息化规划来整合、规范属下各级子公司的信息化建设。建立了公司信息化管控体系，进一步提升了公司信息化的执行力。随着公司的不断发展，信息系统规划也在不断调整以适应新的形势。本案例以广州白云山制药总厂信息化规划的演进作为主线，探讨在广东产业升级的背景下，总厂在每一轮的战略调整中逐步将信息系统规划提到了重要的战略位置上，通过将信息技术融入企业的各个关键业务流程，并利用信息技术对生产和管理活动进行精确控制和精细管理，提高产品质量和附加值，从而加快市场响应速度，支撑企业创新商业模式，提升服务水平，使企业具备较强的市场竞争力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">By the reorganization of Baiyunshan pharmaceutical general factory, they realize that the importance of the enterprise positioning and development of strategic and more awareness the important position of information system planning in enterprise strategy. In &quot; Eleven Five&quot; period, the general factory emphasized integration of information technology and industrialization, advanced energetically integration oriented information system planning, promote mutual infiltration of information and industrialized , has introduced the ERP system, OA system and BQ (business intelligent) system and so on. In 2010, &quot;Twelve Five &quot;information plan of the general factory has been drawn up. Various subsidiaries under the information construction were integrated by the unified information planning. By the establishment of the company’s information management system, the executive force of the company informatiztion was further enhanced. With the continuous development of the company, the planning of information system has been adjusted to adapt to the new situation. According to the main line of the information plan evolution in Guangzhou Baiyunshan pharmaceutical general factory as, the case discussed the information system plan was referred to the important strategic position in every round of the strategic adjustment under the background of the Guangdong industrial upgrading,  so as to accelerate the response speed to the market, supporting enterprise business model innovation, improve service level, make enterprises have strong market competitiveness.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《信息管理系统》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息系统规划与组织战略规划</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-03</td>
                            </tr>
